1. Reseting the commit done in this PR and then,
2. Using the following command.

```
perl -0777 -pi -e 's:((\(|\{|,)(\n| )*)\/\* ?([^=* ]+) ?\*\/ ?:\1/*\4=*/:g' $( git ls-files ./src/test ./src/wallet/test ) src/test/crypto_tests.cpp src/test/util/setup_common.h
```

